FreeRTOS-based firmware for the **TI EK-TM4C123GXL LaunchPad** that reads three I2C sensors, streams telemetry wirelessly over BLE, exposes a UART debug console, logs timestamped records to a circular EEPROM buffer, and supervises all task liveness with a software watchdog layered over the TM4C123 hardware WDT.

