## Hardware

### Bill of Materials

| Component | Part | Notes |
|-----------|------|-------|
| MCU board | TI EK-TM4C123GXL LaunchPad | TM4C123GH6PM · ARM Cortex-M4F · 80 MHz |
| Pressure / temp | BMP180 | I2C addr 0x77 |
| Accel / gyro | MPU6050 | I2C addr 0x68 |
| Magnetometer | QMC5883L / HMC5883L-compatible | I2C addr 0x2C |
| BLE module | HW-290 / AT-09 class (CC2541) | UART passthrough |

### Pin Connections

| Signal | TM4C123 Pin | Peripheral |
|--------|-------------|------------|
| BLE module RX | PE0 (UART0 RX) | BLE UART TX |
| BLE module TX | PE1 (UART0 TX) | BLE UART RX |
| Debug terminal RX | PC4 (UART1 RX) | USB-UART TX |
| Debug terminal TX | PC5 (UART1 TX) | USB-UART RX |
| I2C SDA (all sensors) | PE4 (I2C2 SDA) | BMP180 · MPU6050 · Magnetometer |
| I2C SCL (all sensors) | PE5 (I2C2 SCL) | BMP180 · MPU6050 · Magnetometer |

> All I2C devices share the I2C2 bus. External pull-ups (4.7 kΩ to 3.3 V) are required on SDA and SCL.

