## Sensor Flow

`SENSOR_TASK` supports two acquisition styles:

**One-shot** — command arrives → `process_sensor_mode()` runs once → timers remain stopped.

**Continuous** — command arrives → `xTimerStart()` for both timers → `send_timer` fires every 1 s (`store_enable = false`) → `store_timer` fires every 30 s (`store_enable = true`) → `SENSOR_TASK` wakes via `xTaskNotifyWait()` and dispatches accordingly.

Sensor selection per command:

| Command | Sensor(s) read |
|---------|---------------|
| `SENSORA` / `SENSORA_CONT` | BMP180 (temp + pressure) |
| `SENSORB` / `SENSORB_CONT` | MPU6050 (accel + gyro) |
| `SENSORC` / `SENSORC_CONT` | HMC5883L (heading) |
| `SENSOR_ALL` / `SENSOR_ALL_CONT` | All three |

