## Data Flow Summary

```
BLE receive:
  BLE module → UART0 ISR → uart_ble_rx_buffer → BLE_RECEIVE_TASK
  BLE_RECEIVE_TASK → Ble_commands queue → SENSOR_TASK

BLE send:
  SENSOR_TASK → send_*_ble() formatters → Ble_responses queue
  Ble_responses queue → BLE_SEND_TASK → UART0 TX → BLE module

Debug:
  PC terminal → UART1 ISR → uart_debug_rx_buffer → DEBUG_CONSOLE_TASK
  DEBUG_CONSOLE_TASK → debug_queue → DEBUG_TASK

I2C:
  SENSOR_TASK → I2C driver (mutex) → I2C2 peripheral
  I2C2 ISR → i2c_isr_message queue → i2c_wait() unblocks driver
  timeout → i2c_reinit() → recover_i2c_bus() → retry

Storage:
  SENSOR_TASK (NOTIFY_STORE) → store_sensor_data() → push_to_eeprom()
  → EEPROMProgram() → internal EEPROM circular buffer
```

