| `READ_SENSORA` | One-shot BMP180 read to debug UART |
| `READ_SENSORB` | One-shot MPU6050 read to debug UART |
| `READ_SENSORC` | One-shot magnetometer read to debug UART |
| `READ_ALL_SENSORS` | One-shot read of all three sensors |
| `CALIBRATE_HMC5883L` | Start magnetometer hard-iron calibration |
| `CALIB_STOP` | Stop calibration and apply offsets |
| `display_eeprom` | Dump stored EEPROM records to debug UART |

